  <p>This is an educational overview of LL-37, covering its biology, mechanisms, wound healing properties, vitamin D connection, research status, and safety profile. It is <strong>not a recommendation to use LL-37</strong>. LL-37 is not FDA-approved for therapeutic use. Consult a qualified healthcare provider before considering any peptide protocol.</p>
